                <h2 data-uuid="73c9df07780043f49867975adf8fc2de">Gold Bugs and Silverites</h2>
                <p data-uuid="edc438d9c2904cd2875ef9edd7d8908b">In the late 1800s, a political debate over currency pitted Gold Bugs against Silverites.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
